2023. 10. 10. Thu

Brevet Clock
by psjoy

Count ellapsed time since brevet starts.
Dim timer display if time is expired.

Can select start data/time, brevet kind(distance), start time interval
Starting slot can be added/deleted in status tab

Font size can be adjusted in etc tab.


